Interface Versioned.Ordering

All Known Implementing Classes:
Versioned.After$, Versioned.Before$, Versioned.Concurrent$
Enclosing interface:
Versioned<T>
public static interface Versioned.Ordering

The result of comparing two Versioned objects. Either: 


   1) v1 is BEFORE v2               => Before
   2) v1 is AFTER t2                => After
   3) v1 happens CONCURRENTLY to v2 => Concurrent
